der-gray-800\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center py-4\"><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\" href=\"/uz\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold text-xl\">G</span></div><span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Graver<span class=\"text-teal-500\">.uz</span></span></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center space-x-8\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\"><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz#services\">Xizmatlar</a><div class=\"relative group\"><button class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition flex items-center\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Mahsulotlar<svg class=\"ml-1 w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path></svg></button></div><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz#portfolio\">Portfolio</a><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz#process\">Jarayon</a><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz#faq\">FAQ</a><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/contacts\">Aloqa</a><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 border-l border-gray-700 pl-4\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium transition text-gray-400 hover:text-white\" hrefLang=\"ru\" href=\"/ru\">RU</a><span class=\"text-gray-600\">/</span><a class=\"text-sm font-medium transition text-teal-500\" hrefLang=\"uz\" href=\"/uz\">UZ</a></div></nav><div class=\"hidden md:flex flex-col items-end space-y-1\"><a href=\"tel:+998770802288\" class=\"text-white font-semibold hover:text-teal-500 transition text-sm\">+998 77 080 22 88</a><a href=\"tel:+998974802288\" class=\"text-gray-300 text-xs hover:text-teal-500 transition\">+998 97 480 22 88</a></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-white p-2\" aria-label=\"Открыть меню\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-navigation\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main-content\" class=\"pt-20\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"Zakupщик chek-list: korporativ sovg'alar (8 qadam)\",\"description\":\"Jarayonni xatosiz yuring: brif, maket, ishlab chiqarish, QC, yetkazish. Toshkentda hisob-kitob oling!\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/korporativ-sovgalar-zakupshchik-chek-listi\",\"image\":\"/images/blog/korporativ-sovgalar-zakupshchik-chek-listi.jpg\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-03-03\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-03-03\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/logo192.png\"}},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/korporativ-sovgalar-zakupshchik-chek-listi\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Zakupщик chek-list: korporativ sovg'alar (8 qadam)\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/korporativ-sovgalar-zakupshchik-chek-listi\"}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-8\"><ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-400 flex-wrap gap-y-1\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz\">Graver.uz</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 truncate max-w-xs\">Zakupщик chek-list: korporativ sovg&#x27;alar (8 qadam)</li></ol></nav><header class=\"mb-10\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight\">Zakupщик chek-list: korporativ sovg&#x27;alar (8 qadam)</h1><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-500\"><time dateTime=\"2026-03-03\">2-mart, 2026</time><span>2<!-- --> <!-- -->daqiqa o&#x27;qish</span><span>Graver.uz</span></div></header><div class=\"mb-10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/blog/korporativ-sovgalar-zakupshchik-chek-listi.jpg\" alt=\"Zakupщик chek-list: korporativ sovg&#x27;alar (8 qadam)\" class=\"w-full aspect-video object-cover\" loading=\"eager\"/></div><article class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p>Korporativ sovg&#x27;a xaridi ko&#x27;pincha &quot;oxirgi daqiqada&quot; boshlangan stressli jarayonga aylanadi. Bu chek-list - operatsion: g&#x27;oya emas, jarayon. 8 qadam bilan muddat, sifat va hujjatlarni nazorat qilasiz.</p>\n<h2>1-qadam: Brif (aniqlik - 50% natija)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Auditoriya: xodim/hamkor/mijoz/event</li>\n<li>Tiraj va segment: 1 turmi yoki 2-3 turmi</li>\n<li>Byudjet diapazoni va &quot;must-have&quot;</li>\n<li>Deadline: taqdimot sanasi</li>\n<li>Brend materiallari: logo, rang, shrift</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>2-qadam: Byudjet va risk zaxirasi</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Narx tarkibi: buyum + brending + qadoqlash + komplektatsiya + logistika</li>\n<li>Zaxira: 5-15% (qayta gravirovka/qo&#x27;shimcha dona)</li>\n<li>To&#x27;lov shartlari va hujjatlar (schyot/faktura/akt)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>3-qadam: Yetkazib beruvchini tanlash (10 mezon)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Portfolio va real namuna sifati</li>\n<li>Gravirovka aniqligi (metall/yog&#x27;och)</li>\n<li>Tirajga tayyor quvvat</li>\n<li>QC tizimi bor-yo&#x27;qligi</li>\n<li>Muddatga kafolat</li>\n<li>Hujjatlar, shartnoma</li>\n<li>Qadoqlash imkoniyatlari</li>\n<li>Toshkent bo&#x27;yicha logistika</li>\n<li>Kommunikatsiya tezligi</li>\n<li>Avariya-reja (nima bo&#x27;lsa?)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>4-qadam: Maket va tasdiqlash (xatolar aynan shu yerda)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Logo formati: vektor (SVG/AI/PDF)</li>\n<li>Gravirovka joyi va o&#x27;lchami</li>\n<li>Ismlar ro&#x27;yxati (Excel) + transliteratsiya qoidasi</li>\n<li>Tabrik matni va qadoqlash yorlig&#x27;i</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>5-qadam: Namuna (pilot)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>1-2 dona tayyor namunani ko&#x27;ring</li>\n<li>Kontrast, shrift o&#x27;qiluvchanligi, joylashuv</li>\n<li>Qadoqlash &quot;unboxing&quot; tekshiruvi</li>\n<li>Tasdiq: yozma (chat/email)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>6-qadam: Ishlab chiqarish va monitoring</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Sana reja: kunma-kun</li>\n<li>Oraliq foto/video hisobot</li>\n<li>Segmentlar bo&#x27;yicha komplektatsiya ro&#x27;yxati</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>7-qadam: QC (sifat nazorati)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Namuna bilan solishtirish</li>\n<li>Ismlar xatosi yo&#x27;qligi</li>\n<li>Qadoqlash shikastlanmagan</li>\n<li>Yetishmayotgan pozitsiyalar yo&#x27;q</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>8-qadam: Yetkazib berish va hisobot</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Qabul-berish akti</li>\n<li>Yakuniy ro&#x27;yxat (necha dona, qanday segment)</li>\n<li>Ichki hisobot: byudjet, muddat, feedback</li>\n<li>Keyingi safar uchun &quot;lessons learned&quot;</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Buyurtma bermoqchimisiz?</strong> Telegram <a href=\"https://t.me/graveruz\">@graveruz</a> ga yozing yoki saytdagi shaklni to&#x27;ldiring.</p></article><section class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">O&#x27;xshash maqolalar</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/korporativ-sovgalar-toliq-gid-2025-uzbekistan\">Korporativ sovg&#x27;alar 2025: O&#x27;zbekistonda to&#x27;liq gid</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Xodimlar, hamkorlar va mijozlar uchun sovg&#x27;ani to&#x27;g&#x27;ri tanlang. Byudjet, g&#x27;oya, gravirovka. Hisob-kitob so&#x27;rang!</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/b2b-hamkorlar-uchun-sovgalar-etiket-gid\">B2B sovg&#x27;alar: hamkorlar uchun etiket va tanlov</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Hamkor/mijozga sovg&#x27;a tanlang: status darajalari, taqiqlar, gravirovka. Toshkentda buyurtma qiling!</p></article></div></section><div class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8\"><a class=\"text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-400 transition flex items-center\" href=\"/uz/blog\">← <!-- -->Blogga qaytish</a></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-black border-t border-gray-800 mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\" href=\"/uz\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold\">G</span></div><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Graver<span class=\"text-teal-500\">.uz</span></span></a><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">Toshkentda biznes uchun premium lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik va brendlash</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">Navigatsiya</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz#services\">Xizmatlar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 te